Publication dates of the available zip files

Source: R/psmv-xml-data.R
psmv_xml_dates.Rd

Publication dates of the available zip files

Usage

psmv_xml_dates

Format

character vector of publication dates in the format YYYY-MM-DD

Examples

print(psmv_xml_dates)
